data.description: Charming move-in-ready home located in the North Valley!  Home features 1,351 square feet with 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms! Great living space with beautiful hardwood floors!  Updated bathrooms with beautifully done tile and newer vanities.  This home features a 385 square foot detached workshop and 188 square foot basement.  Good sized backyard perfect for gardening.
